His last album was
a blend of pop songs

00:00:21.490 --> 00:00:23.560
and his concerto for
piano and orchestra

00:00:23.560 --> 00:00:26.620
that soared to number one on
the Billboard classical and

00:00:26.620 --> 00:00:29.289
classical crossover
charts for over a decade.

00:00:29.289 --> 00:00:31.330
He's performed with some
of the greatest symphony

00:00:31.330 --> 00:00:34.910
orchestras in addition to being
a judge on NBC's the "Sing

00:00:34.910 --> 00:00:35.410
Off."

00:00:35.410 --> 00:00:38.890
Continues to have cameos
all over cable network TV.

