[CHEERS AND APPLAUSE]

00:45:15.980 --> 00:45:16.479
Yeah?

00:45:16.479 --> 00:45:17.346
Yeah.

00:45:17.346 --> 00:45:18.880
So a couple people.

00:45:18.880 --> 00:45:19.660
Couple people.

