So I'm a big fan of the
show "You're the Worst,"

00:45:26.440 --> 00:45:29.100
and in particular your
performance on the show.

00:45:29.100 --> 00:45:31.240
And I'm just curious
how you ended up there,

00:45:31.240 --> 00:45:34.150
and any sneak peeks
into the next season?

00:45:34.150 --> 00:45:34.750
Are you alive?

00:45:38.560 --> 00:45:41.880
BEN FOLDS: Has the last one
