00:45:41.880 --> 00:45:44.470
Oh.

00:45:44.470 --> 00:45:45.380
I did another one.

00:45:45.380 --> 00:45:47.046
I'm sure they don't
mind me saying that.

00:45:47.046 --> 00:45:49.580
I think it's towards
the end of the season.

00:45:49.580 --> 00:45:53.410
And yeah, I still have
a pulse in this one.

00:45:53.410 --> 00:45:56.080
And we've also talked
about if it ever

00:45:56.080 --> 00:46:02.950
goes further, how close we
can get to me not being alive.

00:46:02.950 --> 00:46:04.660
But for anyone
