00:46:24.280 --> 00:46:28.660
creates this weird little
world where, for some reason,

00:46:28.660 --> 00:46:30.940
they don't have mixed
drinks in North Carolina.

00:46:30.940 --> 00:46:34.760
I'm like, wow, you
can get alcohol here.

